I enjoyed watching them.  Great entertainment.  My one issue with the movie is that when Frank Vega holds up his dress uniform.  In the story line, he said he was in Vietnam 7 years and would have probably stayed longer if he had not got shot.  His class A jacket has his purple heart pinned on it and is cool, except that the uniform has a First Sergeants rank on the sleeve, and an infantry officers brass on the collar.  I know it is comedy but there is just something wrong about a uniform screw up.

These 2 movies are great entertainment and fun to watch.
danny glover and danny trejo at their best and funniest
